title: Tomb of the Chaos
story: The tomb is situated on a remote shore. Now it is controlled by a party of cultists.

notes.text: A fresco on the wall, totally destroyed by cultist vandals.
A scorched gate with a keyhole to the east.
A large pile of rubble hides an ornate javelin and a scarf.
A stuffed dwarf with a key in their hands.
A corpse of a cultist, a silver mirror nearby.
